<section id="fundador" class="section founder noise">
  <div class="container founder__grid">
    <div class="founder__image-col reveal">
      <div class="founder__image-frame">
        <img
          src="/founder-tavares.webp"
          alt="Guilherme Tavares, fundador da GTech e criador da Hausly"
          class="founder__photo"
          loading="lazy"
          width="480"
          height="480"
        />
        <div class="founder__image-accent"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="founder__content reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <span class="kicker">Quem está por trás</span>
      <h2>Nasceu de conversas reais<br />com corretores em Goiânia</h2>

      <div class="founder__bio">
        <p>
          Criada por <strong>Guilherme Tavares</strong>, fundador da
          <strong>GTech</strong>, depois de ouvir dezenas de corretores contarem
          a mesma história: lead sumindo, visita furando, planilha abandonada.
        </p>
        <p>
          A resposta não era mais um CRM genérico — era uma ferramenta para
          quem vende na rua, celular na mão, precisando de velocidade, não de burocracia.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="founder__brand">
        <div class="founder__brand-badge">
          <img
            src="/logo-gtech.webp"
            alt="GTech"
            class="founder__gtech-logo"
            loading="lazy"
            width="48"
            height="48"
          />
          <div>
            <strong>GT Tecnologia e Serviços LTDA</strong>
            <span>Setor Marista, Goiânia — GO · Desde 2022</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="founder__cnpj">CNPJ 46.112.388/0001-13</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .founder {
    background: var(--navy-900);
    color: var(--white);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .founder .kicker {
    color: var(--amber-light);
  }

  .founder .kicker::before {
    background: var(--amber-light);
  }

  .founder h2 {
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .founder__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.45fr 0.55fr;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .founder__image-frame {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    max-width: 420px;
  }

  .founder__photo {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    filter: grayscale(0.1) contrast(1.05);
    transition: filter var(--duration-slow);
  }

  .founder__image-frame:hover .founder__photo {
    filter: grayscale(0) contrast(1);
  }

  .founder__image-accent {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: inherit;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to top,
      rgba(12, 18, 34, 0.6) 0%,
      transparent 40%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .founder__bio {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .founder__bio p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--slate-300);
  }

  .founder__bio strong {
    color: var(--white);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .founder__brand {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding-top: var(--space-lg);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--navy-600);
  }

  .founder__brand-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding: 12px 20px 12px 12px;
    background: var(--navy-800);
    border: 1px solid var(--navy-600);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .founder__gtech-logo {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    object-fit: contain;
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 4px;
  }

  .founder__brand-badge strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .founder__brand-badge span {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--slate-400);
  }

  .founder__cnpj {
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    color: var(--slate-500);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .founder__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
    }

    .founder__image-frame {
      max-width: 320px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }
</style>
